import React from 'react'; import { Article, Card, Code, Button, Heading, Image, Layout, Link, Paragraph, Section, UnorderedList, OrderedList } from 'dropship-components'; //import imageURL from './dropship.png'; // http://avatars.adorable.io const dropshipLogo = 'https://api.adorable.io/avatars/285/dropship.png'; import './App.scss'; const dropshipGithubLink = 'https://github.com/jasonrundell/dropship'; const dropshipDemoGithubLink = 'https://github.com/jasonrundell/dropship-demo'; const goToDropshipDemoGithub = (event) => { event.preventDefault(); location.href = dropshipDemoGithubLink; } const goToDropshipGithub = (event) => { event.preventDefault(); location.href = dropshipGithubLink; } const App = () => Dropship

Ordered List <OrderedList items={['One','Two','Three']} />

Link {dropshipGithubLink} <Link cssClass="color__alt" href={dropshipGithubLink} onClick={goToDropshipGithub}>{dropshipGithubLink}</Link>
